Mistakes And Problems Every Freelancer Face: Setting Project Scope In The Beginning

* Client ke saath jab apki chat ho toh sbse pehla kaam yeh kijiye kay ap project ka scope define kijiye.

* Agar ap project ka scope define nhi krte ap ,project ke beech mein pesa lossk rte hai, time loss krte hai, or ek potential employer/client bhi loss krtein hai. Lekin ap ne Deliverables tey nahi kiye,milestones tey nahi kiye like Project Details, Design Preview,Project Deadline,Payment etc.Toh nuqsaan kiya hua, " Dono ko zaaya waqt zzya hugya ".

* Example of Project Scope: Kay ek service ap 100$ ki provide krrahay hai,toh mein client ko bataonga kay ek specific time lagega service ko deliver krne mein

* " How Much Time It Will Take To Complete The Assignment ".
* " Determine The Scope ". // Price Batayein
* " Fight For Right ".
* " Value Proposition ". // Apni worth batyein